"msg":"我岩岩都係咁<br />\n離遠見到架𨋢點解咁耐都唔關<br />\n心諗係咪超載<br />\n行到埋去先知冇人關門<br />\n即刻入去做陪企師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455bca98d3411baa0226fad01a986f2de7a37ec7","tid":2140863,"uid":7529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c009a529b1dae5a2cf4245f5ffdd40c70be00b4","tid":2140863,"uid":2267,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:43:15.000Z","msg":"早幾日返屋企，去到樓下門口撳密碼前，我隔離有個師奶，我心諗一係你撳，我開門或掉轉，見佢無乜意慾撳密碼，我咪走去撳，撳完等佢開門。<br />\n屌佢老味，個師奶真係唔郁唔去開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咪同佢鬥企，直到有人出，我Zip咗埋去入咗半身迫佢用手拉門，最後佢都係唔用手，門又好快閂埋咗，個師奶仍然喺門外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有去廁所鬥洗手／整頭／抹面唔開門"},{"pid":"c961479e378c4321941c9b8a2d3eb867d861f0be","tid":2140863,"uid":13032,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得𨋢掣唔撳冇咩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前去留學啲人都係興唔撳掣<br />\n撳咗好似好趕時間咁好冇禮物<br />\n返到嚟香港未有肺炎之前一個人搭𨋢都係慣咗唔撳改唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正佢都會自己閂<br />\n反而企喺到等人開門啲賤種真係好撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有次老遠見到門後面有個師奶企喺到等我開，我谷鳩氣一嘢大力推開撞撚到佢嘭一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好爽"},{"pid":"acfea7975a4440969558d9fa026ad0dfbaac0e8f","tid":2140863,"uid":96909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"樓下拉門都係啦 ， on 撚鳩自私閪， 香港人以為自己好撚高質， 咩基因心照啦"},{"pid":"bb5f846bf28793dee00b0a27649e36b88200867b","tid":2140863,"uid":170786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"cited