ttps://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200212%2FVD6PQLRPQ2IUBETQJ3X5AWAO3Q%2F&h=40ffbe59\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200212/VD6PQLRPQ2IUBETQJ3X5AWAO3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"cff3996ef5346428b19c6cd25682fc3ac52bb212","tid":2140863,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"頭先番屋企都係咁<br />\n老遠見到個女人係大門前揾紙巾<br />\n我行到去都仲未揾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6fde7b744c4985ad906ec193244f8ae81dc34e","tid":2140863,"uid":128974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"疫情開始果陣已經袋支冇芯既掣出街噤lift同開門"},{"pid":"89e28bfaf3ca11ddf783e711d2e0ee092a9d1404","tid":2140863,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>d 臭西港女好鍾意等人按lift/開門架</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2ab4b6dac17b95bc6d713da35cac7545f98d1e35","tid":2140863,"uid":120776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"自鳩師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8894dc72ae6568cf9b7195c9baf6d878f268c7bf","tid":2140863,"uid":43954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"試過有個師奶同我同lift落樓,住得高過我既<br />\n我一入lift就即刻由lift掣個個位縮埋去斜角落度,都算啦 ,我遲入lift我咪閂門囉<br />\n之後條友就拎張紙巾出黎掩住個口罩<br />\n落到地下條仆街仲要爭住出lift <br />\n然後去到大閘就收步企係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我鬧左句: 咁撚驚就咪撚出去啦屌 , 開到勁窄咁自己攝出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"a2aab691fece3ea5555f051274b37f59186fb7fe","tid":2140863,"uid":17945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d4fda64dab395b4d927e522ebaf961ab0052f0e","tid":2140863,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:23:23.000Z","msg":"左右兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個打機扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一個直頭另轉塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我企後面,心諗唔撳大家齊齊唔好走,我又唔撳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後等到出面有人入黎,個位新入既人先撳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"撳晒所有之後行返出去"},{"pid":"329d21fa3a6a2698d2666f38a8f9d599a64f47c5","tid":2140863,"uid":137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"好多臭閪一入𨋢就玩電話，老馮等人禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ed67520d5e72beab7ac1ec685a2f7ae693c28f","tid":2140863,"uid":30037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"自鳩師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746039ad76a78a25d86c75ea8f5cd4d6be105e3d","tid":2140863,"uid":36050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"早幾日返工時間試過，個師奶最遲入𨋢唔撚撳，ok，落到去我開完門勁快ban埋 條傻閪睇住我出去 自己禁制開啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9e26a5edd51d928ffa91e689945520f2d293b3a1","tid":2140863,"uid":241357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"講起撳𨋢 就真係多野玩<br />\n記得有個人住高層<br />\n驚死比人知佢住邊<br />\n最後一個走左佢先撳<br />\n<br />\n有次比我發現左呢樣野<br />\n再下一次既時候 <br />\n除左我地兩個仲有一個喺𨋢<br />\n果位低層出左𨋢<br />\n終於同佢單對單<br />\n所謂狹路相逢勇者勝<br />\n我就撳我自己果層<br />\n佢不動如山 以守待攻<br />\n去到我果層時<br />\n我就情智急生<br />\n當年啲𨋢雖然有閘刀但係冇紅外開關<br />\n我先龍盤虎踞等部𨋢門開<br />\n心中一路數住時間<br />\n去到出𨋢時環臂撳實個關門制<br />\n剛好出曬個人果下<br />\n𨋢門已經關至一隻半手臂粗既闊度<br />\n我立即抽出隻手<br />\n一路望住部𨋢既顯示落翻去<br />\n一邊聽住佢「哎吔，點解落翻去既」夾雜住幾下摺聲既回響<br />\n嘴角亦不其然微微上揚"},{"pid":"c8dfb829ae93b8cc78c54a8aaae669e7ae3aec79","tid":2140863,"uid":78165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"通常越謹慎嘅人越容易中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417a631a861f87163d94d87d582d178846409ba2","tid":2140863,"uid":274432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"做得好呀， 好撚多自私撚第一個入都唔撚撳屌你老母"}]}